  "2026-04-26T14:04:43.744Z",cursor-agent,"Weekly GitHub findings review 2026-04-26: Triaged 8 Dependabot PRs. Closed 4 stale/superseded PRs (#5 upload-artifact v7 already on main, #6 setup-node v6 already on main, #7 checkout v6 already on main, #9 undici superseded by #15). Applied remaining 4 changes directly on main: bumped pnpm/action-setup v5->v6 in all 3 workflows (#16), bumped softprops/action-gh-release v2->v3 in release workflow (#18), updated undici to 8.1.0 and dev-deps to latest (#15/#19). Fixed ci-workflow-contract test for v3 action ref. All 8 PRs now closed."
